<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Money Machine | Under Maintenance</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(0,255,170,0.18), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #07140f 0%, #0b1f18 45%, #030806 100%);
      color: #f5fff8;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .wrap {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 780px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(9, 20, 16, 0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.18);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 42px 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      text-align: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.24);
      color: #7effca;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .accent {
      color: #7effca;
      text-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(126, 255, 202, 0.28);
    }

    p {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #d7e8dd;
    }

    .small {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #9fb7aa;
    }

    .actions {
      margin-top: 28px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d48a, #41ffb4);
      color: #03110a;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
      color: #f5fff8;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .status {
      margin-top: 26px;
      padding-top: 22px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #a8c2b4;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .card {
        padding: 34px 22px;
        border-radius: 22px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <section class="card">
      <div class="badge">Money Machine Update</div>
      <h1><span class="accent">Money Machine</span><br />is getting upgraded</h1>
      <p>
        We are behind the scenes tightening things up, improving performance, and getting everything ready.
        The site will be back soon.
      </p>
      <p class="small">
        We are making updates so your experience is smoother, cleaner, and better than before.
      </p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Check Back Soon</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Support</a>
      </div>

      <div class="status">
        Status: Maintenance in progress.
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
